    <div id="cookie-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">&times;</span>
            <h3>Cookie設定</h3>
            <p>各Cookieの使用を個別に設定できます。</p>
            <label><input type="checkbox" id="session-cookie" checked> セッションCookie (ログイン管理)</label><br>
            <label><input type="checkbox" id="oauth-cookie" checked> Google OAuth Cookie (認証)</label><br>
            <label><input type="checkbox" id="access-cookie" checked> アクセスCookie (ログ管理)</label><br>
            <label><input type="checkbox" id="adsense-cookie" checked> AdSense Cookie (広告)</label><br>
